Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.54,0:01:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.45,0:01:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把总士还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.79,0:02:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.47,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第24话 对话——核之器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.23,0:02:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.05,0:02:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要和核之器对抗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.42,0:02:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.38,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据修复作业进度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.37,0:03:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计不久CDC可以恢复70%的机能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.48,0:03:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M block虽然基本处于全灭状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.47,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要设施以及block的修复正在顺利进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.59,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军的两极同时正面作战呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.73,0:03:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 要把那个系统移植到法弗尼尔内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然刚开始就很不顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 是要我这把老骨头也带上阵吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.44,0:03:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统的调整让我来作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.11,0:03:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让菲斯特姆那些家伙尝尝卫他们受到的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.47,0:03:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们不是用来复仇的工具啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.89,0:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连千沙都和手塚也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.02,0:04:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.95,0:04:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不会死」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一定会遵守诺言」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想战斗也不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.09,0:04:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想照彩乃所希望的去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.77,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 都是因为我太害怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而使妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一接触到山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像趴在爸爸的背上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.76,0:05:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那种感觉已经消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使听说爸爸可能已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么实感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.60,0:05:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能以后再也不会来这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.99,0:05:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑为什么喜欢这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我 是我妈妈喜欢这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人要从北极回来了是不是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 去确认一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样留在岛上也行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见会不会也留下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑去的话 我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没披好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.20,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望远见能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.50,0:06:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我没有能安慰一骑的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.46,0:06:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是去要老师家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 刚才和剑司商量之后决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.50,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不要任何人死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我决一胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.77,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤 一骑的身体还…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.60,0:06:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到人类军侦察机的信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战斗请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向他们传达我们会参加的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求识别码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.76,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.13,0:06:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也可以驾驶诺顿模型了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.26,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移植到你体内的因子已经稳定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.71,0:07:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我检查一下身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.76,0:07:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取消参加那种战斗吧 真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.19,0:07:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经包围了整个地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像光博所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快除了战斗别无他法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.98,0:07:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们作盾牌来保护孩子们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.24,0:07:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑想一个人去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.62,0:07:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了替皆城总士报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子活不长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.49,0:07:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶不上远见老师的研究了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的时间多少还有点价值吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音在的话你要怎么辩解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这种人找不出其它方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.35,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至都没有活着回来的理由吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.66,0:08:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.64,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良要是看到了一定会大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对弱小的男生没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.34,0:08:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良喜欢像自己父亲一样的男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.33,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 我也能像卫那样变强吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.46,0:08:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.85,0:08:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目标正在接近岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断定为斯芬克司型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的可能性很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持伪装镜面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.75,0:08:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护墙展开准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员全员待机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护墙输出最大功率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌人侵蚀的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与岛的本体分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.47,0:09:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动FENRIR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.92,0:09:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它们尝尝岛的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出现一台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认出现在2点方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个出现的家伙是诱饵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来出现的那台向刚刚的目标前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映像来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.51,0:09:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示在主屏幕上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.97,0:09:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.82,0:09:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲斯特姆之间在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一击就把核破坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的那台消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜索敌人的质量反应消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护墙自动解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.42,0:10:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们还会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.70,0:10:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你们谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山上等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁红音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音  小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.10,0:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里构成的物质和我没有任何关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.47,0:11:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被过去的记忆引导来此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.37,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你已经了解了人类的记忆这个东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.22,0:11:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想见的人来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲斯特姆 什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么企图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.87,0:11:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲斯特姆怎么可能自相残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门断定为「master」型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,master型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类模样的菲斯特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说菲斯特姆内部分裂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如自身达到极限值也可能导致这种情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个对于吾等来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引导向更加未知的解答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.77,0:11:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知的解答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与人类同化的吾等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少能够形成人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.83,0:11:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能立刻布满全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有真壁红音这个存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何逐渐形成了独自的共鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.54,0:12:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过是微小的变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.93,0:12:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对全身产生影响需要10年左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.39,0:12:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 大量的因子与她产生共鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.95,0:12:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使吾等产生了某种时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.36,0:12:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间对吾等来说只不过是形成世界重力之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.91,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真壁红音的存在与大量的核产生共鸣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.36,0:12:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等内部的时间形成了绝对时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有红音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.90,0:12:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几亿的人口牺牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.70,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这点现在吾等正在讨论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.07,0:12:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极限值上已经得出了现象结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.37,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真壁红音自己希望同化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再说一遍看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.53,0:12:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然对于真壁红音来说这是个突发事态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她在和吾等接触的瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受了吾等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝福了吾等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.82,0:13:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等的显现是根据你们的存在所表现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.48,0:13:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等的同化行为和破坏行为\N都是对宇宙所存在的事物的祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.71,0:13:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都被真壁红音逆转了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.39,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是第一个理解我们的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.50,0:13:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实体化的菲斯特姆全体是由硅素源形成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个宇宙里最深奥的物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是泥土罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.31,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城她们正努力分析核之器的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.59,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁队长正一边玩弄泥土一边理解菲斯特姆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.53,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和它们对话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝木也来试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.65,0:13:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样抚摸泥土的话总有一天\N你可能会明白菲斯特姆的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.76,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对与我相近的你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.10,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我相连的最重要的核\N和真壁红音的共鸣核是所有问题的解答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被北极的核之器夺走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.19,0:14:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们能拯救那个即将被毁灭的核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.68,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要杀了自己的同伴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来吾等全体是同一的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.03,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是「无」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在于任何地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此不可能分裂也不可能互相消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.58,0:14:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真壁红音使我们逆转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成了一道痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.81,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为真壁红音理解了吾等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就这样开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.40,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她向不存在的我们祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.05,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与核之器对抗形成了一个存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不存在的你们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.95,0:14:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.80,0:14:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为真壁红音意识的连接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.82,0:14:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.32,0:15:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着核之器的内部所剩下的核的消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.49,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是只好作为最初不存在的事物而消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.50,0:15:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音现在也在和菲斯特姆对话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.73,0:15:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的共鸣越来越大继续影响着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在人类和核之器互相毁灭之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.69,0:15:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们来接触我的核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里能给你们需要的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲斯特姆给我们的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.79,0:15:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说把从我们这里夺去的生命还给我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等也是不能操作时间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.70,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果是时间的重力还未到达的未来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以和我们共有你们想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.59,0:15:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把数据给他看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.19,0:15:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等没有所谓的数据概念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话一定能行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.56,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据送过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太庞大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能缩小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到主电脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经自动送过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.12,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么送过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.13,0:16:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从菲斯特姆的攻击中得来的机体保护方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.79,0:16:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日野洋治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是以一个人打倒大量的菲斯特姆为胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是应该一个人救出大量的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是日野洋治的设计理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体和菲斯特姆融合的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从遗传因子水平得来的内置机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至有意识水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和菲斯特姆共存了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.12,0:16:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我能交给你们的只有这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.06,0:16:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多数的答案可在核之器内得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到大家的理解就够了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是救出了你们的核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员们能获救吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.36,0:16:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们肉体上的同化现象只不过是处于最初阶段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.41,0:16:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁红音的共鸣核正在引导将来更多的解答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.87,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎样才能到达激战地和核之器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最合适的方法已经送过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.83,0:17:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据这个接近核之器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.23,0:17:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来由我的核来引导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.74,0:17:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们被夺走的东西中能取回一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们称为齐格菲的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.78,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核之器想获得你们的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.83,0:17:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但吾等无法使用它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.13,0:17:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以核之器让会使用的人类生存了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.98,0:17:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是系统的搭乘者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.21,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.43,0:17:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫皆城总士的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士…还活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.10,0:17:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是想毁灭没有同化你们的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.28,0:17:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量重力源反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.91,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10 20…还在增长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核之器正渴求阿尔比斯的核
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.99,0:17:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛由吾等来保护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.16,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.66,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.08,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令他来这里的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以自己相近的存在为基础
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择了战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋 甲洋 春日井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了岛我接受你的提议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相都能发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.06,0:18:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用红音的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是最好的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.01,0:18:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想传达给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.81,0:18:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.62,0:19:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我抚养了一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.00,0:19:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力源反应一个接一个消灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音老师告诉我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化现象的抗体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.46,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良也使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短时间内就见效了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.48,0:19:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分割了齐格菲系统的原型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已内置到四台法弗尼尔中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.64,0:19:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用这个全员都可以进入相位操作状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以同步动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人担心的驾驶员生理问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据「master」型带来的数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.35,0:19:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.06,0:19:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员全部都要感谢真壁红音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在这个装备中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有2个缺点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.56,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是全员要共有大家的痛楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.70,0:19:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士承担了我们所有人的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要承担给他看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.53,0:20:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个是有一台要是出事的话都会给系统带来伤亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.16,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个也不准死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是去死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起活着回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.12,0:20:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么确认机体编码和驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛因号 真壁一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈特号 近藤剑司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.04,0:20:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉奔号 远见真矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.73,0:20:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱号 加侬.曼弗斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坐咲良的机体…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10小时以内完成调度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于北极的核之器决战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.23,0:20:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接触特定的核之器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.83,0:20:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 夺回皆城总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是这次作战的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战代号怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.01,0:20:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军在寻求大气圈外的出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.73,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起名为「Heaven's Door」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「通往天国之门」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真做作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.46,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔能去到天国吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.05,0:21:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们叫「天空」怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.57,0:21:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战日外界的天气是晴天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 称为「苍穹」怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.90,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍穹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝辽阔的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.19,0:21:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始16小时以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始「苍穹」作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在山丘上等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.37,0:21:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活着回来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以叫你妈妈吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你回来 加侬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30年不见的自然受孕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这样遵守着约定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.92,0:21:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要告诉将出生的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.61,0:21:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路还长着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.38,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.99,0:22:11.22,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 回来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.22,0:22:13.23,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你教我一些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.23,0:22:14.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.84,0:22:16.99,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,触摸泥土的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.99,0:22:18.49,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧制陶盆的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.06,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会教你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.06,0:22:24.18,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从你妈妈那里学来的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.23,0:22:28.02,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.08,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 手臂借来用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.48,0:22:38.51,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.80,0:22:42.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 下一个 近藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.42,0:22:45.36,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么符咒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.36,0:22:47.87,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是龙宫岛的坐标吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.87,0:22:48.77,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.77,0:22:51.67,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会活着回来的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.67,0:22:52.75,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加侬也来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.75,0:22:54.25,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.36,0:22:56.59,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.59,0:22:58.06,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.47,0:23:01.82,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的由我来画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.06,0:23:04.34,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.84,0:23:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.14,0:23:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.31,0:23:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.35,0:23:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的正义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.31,0:23:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活着回到岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.68,0:23:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  苍穹的Fafnir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.53,0:23:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终话 天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.34,0:23:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗


